{
  "stem": "1338.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I don't know, maybe 10, 15 of us went to that place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked there for several months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember I worked there in '43 still because my father-- when my father died, I was still in that plant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I started working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "About two months later, I went to work for a statistical office, which was running statistics.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everything is very well organized in Germany and in the ghetto that's run by-- so we had some statistical office, and I became a runner sort of, one of those guys who delivers things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then that was closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was-- actually, Runkowski came in to liquidate it, and he was told by my boss that I finished high school-- finished high school age of 16.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We finished high school at 16, then I had two more years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he turned to me with a smile and said, hey, you got my diploma.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I'll send you to a good place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He sent me to a place which was a company that made-- factory that made telephones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was inclined always to engineering and to things like that, so I enjoyed it very much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was treated very well and very nice people there, mostly more educated kids, either from my school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A bunch of them came from Prague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember I became very friendly with a whole bunch of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And some of them were communists, actually, and active in sabotage and in all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know if you want me to describe some of the events of that time, just to give a feeling of that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "From there on I went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had, for example-- it's a very strange group of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
